; Similar to Kojo's ColorMaker.radialGradient function
to kojoRadialGradient :x :y :color1 :radius :color2 :cyclic?
	localmake "colorStops createPList2 [
		[0 :color1] [1 :color2]
	]
	localmake "spreadMethod "pad
	if :cyclic? [
		localmake "spreadMethod "repeat
	]
	output createRadialGradient2 [:x :y] [:x :y] :radius :colorStops :spreadMethod
end